headline: C&S sues Kroger over $125M termination fee
summary: The wholesaler alleges that the grocer has declined to pay it the agreed-upon fee related to the failure of the Kroger-Albertsons merger.

headline: Kroger cuts jobs at 84.51°
summary: The layoffs at the grocer’s retail analytics subsidiary reflect an effort by the company to “focus on the key priorities that power our go-to-market strategy,” a spokesperson said.
